Global Oncolytic Virus Drug Treatment Market Insights
Oncolytic Virus Drug Treatment Market size was valued at USD 4.3 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 11.8 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 16.6% from 2024 to 2030.

Oncolytic Virus Drug Treatment Market Overview
The global Oncolytic Virus Drug Treatment Market is projected to reach a market value of USD 1.2 billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 20% from 2025 to 2030. The increasing prevalence of cancer and the rising demand for innovative therapies that can target and destroy cancer cells with minimal side effects is driving market growth. Technological advancements in genetic engineering and the growing number of clinical trials are expected to fuel market expansion. Additionally, rising healthcare investments and regulatory approvals for oncolytic virus therapies are contributing to a positive market outlook.

